 STORE</span></a><meta property="position" content="1"></span> &gt; <span property="itemListElement" typeof="ListItem"><span property="name" class="post post-page current-item">Rangi Paint Store 404 Error</span><meta property="url" content="https://rangi.co.ke/rangi-paint-store-4o4-error-page/"><meta property="position" content="2"></span></div> <!-- .breadcrumb : NavXT --></div></div> </header><div id="main" class="clearfix"><div class="inner-wrap"><div id="primary"><div id="content" class="clearfix"> <article id="post-1000" class="post-1000 page type-page status-publish has-post-thumbnail hentry"><div class="entry-content clearfix"><h1 class="has-text-align-center wp-block-heading">SORRY</h1><p class="has-text-align-center">We couldn&#8217;t find that page</p><p class="has-text-align-center">Try searching or go to <a href="https://rangi.co.ke/">Rangi Paint Store&#8217;s home page</a></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" width="620" height="369" src="https://rangi.co.ke/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/error.png" alt="" class="wp-image-1001"/></figure></div> <footer class="entry-meta-bar clearfix"><div class="entry-meta clearfix"></div> </footer> </article></div><!-- #content --></div><!-- #primary --></div><!-- .inner-wrap --></div><!-- #main --><footer id="colophon" class="clearfix"><div class="footer-widgets-wrapper"><div class="inner-wrap"><div class="footer-widgets-area clearfix"><div class="tg-one-half"> <aside id="text-1" class="widget widget_text"><h3 class="widget-title"><span>About Us</span></h3><div class="textwidget"><p>Rangi Paint Store provide a wide selection of crown paints, dura coat paints and plascon paints for sale. We also provide affordable painting services in kenya.</p><p>We have trained experts who can ease you through any painting project with the right tools and colours. We&#8217;re here for you. so let us know what we can do to make your painting experience more enjoyable.</p><p><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Get Paint Today</span></strong></p><p>Whether you’re giving your home’s interior a fresh coat or you’re painting an entire home exterior, Rangi Paint Store is ready to get you the paint products and supplies you need. <a href="https://rangi.co.ke/contact/">Contact us today</a> by calling 0<em><strong>725 326 795</strong></em> to speak with a professional who can assist you.</p><p><img decoding="async" src="https://rangi.co.ke/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/lipa-na-mpesa-till-no1.png" /></p></div> </aside></div><div class="tg-one-half tg-one-half-last"> <aside id="text-3" class="widget widget_text"><h3 class="widget-title"><span>The Premier Paint Store in Nairobi</span></h3><div class="textwidget"><p>Sometimes, all it takes to beautify something is a fresh coat of paint. <a href="https://rangi.co.ke">Rangi Paint Store</a> provides you with a complete array of painting resources, to make sure you have everything you need to lay on the perfect coat!</p><p>As your premier paint store in Nairobi, we carry just about anything you need to get started with your painting project.</p><p>And much more! You just need to come in and check us out.</p><p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Please Subscribe to our Newsletter</strong></span></p> <script>(function() {
